text: Moe Nakata (born 2 June 1991) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2014 FINA Women's Water Polo World League and 2015 World Aquatic Championships. == References == == Other websites == * fina recap day 7 waterpolo * womens-intercontinental-tournament-day-3 Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
